{"thag13.1:0.1":"Theragatha 13.1 ","thag13.1:0.2":"Terasanipata ","thag13.1:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag13.1:0.4":"Sonakolivisattheragatha ","thag13.1:1.1":"“Yahu ratthe samukkattho, ","thag13.1:1.2":"ranno angassa paddhagu; ","thag13.1:1.3":"Svajja dhammesu ukkattho, ","thag13.1:1.4":"sono dukkhassa paragu. ","thag13.1:2.1":"Panca chinde panca jahe, ","thag13.1:2.2":"panca cuttari bhavaye; ","thag13.1:2.3":"Panca sangatigo bhikkhu, ","thag13.1:2.4":"oghatinnoti vuccati. ","thag13.1:3.1":"Unnalassa pamattassa, ","thag13.1:3.2":"bahirasassa bhikkhuno; ","thag13.1:3.3":"Silam samadhi panna ca, ","thag13.1:3.4":"paripurim na gacchati. ","thag13.1:4.1":"Yanhi kiccam apaviddham, ","thag13.1:4.2":"akiccam pana kariyati; ","thag13.1:4.3":"Unnalanam pamattanam, ","thag13.1:4.4":"tesam vaddhanti asava. ","thag13.1:5.1":"Yesanca susamaraddha, ","thag13.1:5.2":"niccam kayagata sati; ","thag13.1:5.3":"Akiccam te na sevanti, ","thag13.1:5.4":"kicce sataccakarino; ","thag13.1:5.5":"Satanam sampajananam, ","thag13.1:5.6":"attham gacchanti asava. ","thag13.1:6.1":"Ujumaggamhi akkhate, ","thag13.1:6.2":"gacchatha ma nivattatha; ","thag13.1:6.3":"Attana codayattanam, ","thag13.1:6.4":"nibbanamabhiharaye. ","thag13.1:7.1":"Accaraddhamhi viriyamhi, ","thag13.1:7.2":"sattha loke anuttaro; ","thag13.1:7.3":"Vinopamam karitva me, ","thag13.1:7.4":"dhammam desesi cakkhuma; ","thag13.1:7.5":"Tassaham vacanam sutva, ","thag13.1:7.6":"vihasim sasane rato. ","thag13.1:8.1":"Samatham patipadesim, ","thag13.1:8.2":"uttamatthassa pattiya; ","thag13.1:8.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","thag13.1:8.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thag13.1:9.1":"Nekkhamme adhimuttassa, ","thag13.1:9.2":"pavivekanca cetaso; ","thag13.1:9.3":"Abyapajjadhimuttassa, ","thag13.1:9.4":"upadanakkhayassa ca. ","thag13.1:10.1":"Tanhakkhayadhimuttassa, ","thag13.1:10.2":"asammohanca cetaso; ","thag13.1:10.3":"Disva ayatanuppadam, ","thag13.1:10.4":"samma cittam vimuccati. ","thag13.1:11.1":"Tassa samma vimuttassa, ","thag13.1:11.2":"santacittassa bhikkhuno; ","thag13.1:11.3":"Katassa paticayo natthi, ","thag13.1:11.4":"karaniyam na vijjati. ","thag13.1:12.1":"Selo yatha ekagghano, ","thag13.1:12.2":"vatena na samirati; ","thag13.1:12.3":"Evam rupa rasa sadda, ","thag13.1:12.4":"gandha phassa ca kevala. ","thag13.1:13.1":"Ittha dhamma anittha ca, ","thag13.1:13.2":"nappavedhenti tadino; ","thag13.1:13.3":"Thitam cittam visannuttam, ","thag13.1:13.4":"vayancassanupassati”ti. ","thag13.1:13.5":"… Sono koliviso thero … ","thag13.1:13.6":"Terasanipato nitthito. ","thag13.1:14.0":"Tatruddanam ","thag13.1:14.1":"Sono koliviso thero, ","thag13.1:14.2":"ekoyeva mahiddhiko; ","thag13.1:14.3":"Terasamhi nipatamhi, ","thag13.1:14.4":"gathayo cettha terasati. "}